  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/1306",
  "title": "NumericRefinementList and Range distinction",
  "body": "Our NumericRefinementList has it's own namespace while this is a Range with multiple start/end values and a possible multiple/single element selected behavior.\n\nI don't know yet how to make this easier. I find it weird that we have both NumericRefinementList and Range. A NumericRefinementList is a Range dealing with multiple ranges. So we either have a naming issue or we need to merge them.\n\nMaybe we can just rename NumericRefinementList to MultiRange?\n",
